comment:
* This class is used by the assistant application to know what went wrong during using
 * {@link VisualQueryDetectionService} and which action that the application should take.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: ERROR_CODE_UNKNOWN
variables.comment: * An error code which means an unknown error occurs.

variables.name: ERROR_CODE_BIND_FAILURE
variables.comment: * Indicates that the system server binds visual query detection service failure.

variables.name: ERROR_CODE_BINDING_DIED
variables.comment: * Indicates that the visual query detection service is dead.

variables.name: ERROR_CODE_ILLEGAL_ATTENTION_STATE
variables.comment: * Indicates that the detection service has no attention listener registered.

variables.name: ERROR_CODE_ILLEGAL_STREAMING_STATE
variables.comment: * Indicates that the detection service is not egressing and should not be streaming queries.

variables.name: ERROR_CODE_REMOTE_EXCEPTION
variables.comment: * Indicates that the remote exception occurs when calling callback method.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel dest, int flags)
